{"tid":523434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又一球][幾時按章工作]休班警揸車撞傷單車男 涉危駕被捕","createTime":"2018-01-08T14:19:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T05:58:05.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cd7a9df72de2643bb95d77fb96f38a09d23a5e22","tid":523434,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T14:19:09.000Z","msg":"尖沙嘴去年7月15日下午發生一宗交通意外，當日44歲姓陳男子駕駛私家車由港威大道右轉入停車場時，意外撞倒一部單車，單車上的55歲姓張男子腳部受傷，由救護車送伊利沙伯醫院治理。警方到場調查，證實陳為一名休班警，案件交西九龍總區交通部意外調查隊第五隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n警方經深入調查及徵詢法律意見後，昨日於紅磡區拘捕陳，並控告他一項危險駕駛引致他人身體受嚴重傷害罪。案件將於本周五(12日)在九龍城裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180108/57682879\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180108%2F57682879&d=S5hC4lpB7aC5S1kjtA%2FrctibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=4ed6d5b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180108%2F57682879&h=eb8e9db1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180108/57682879</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n讓夠你當班警5球，我睇你點追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f7b7d9c298b3c6b3b08208fd6d10413aec1d08","tid":523434,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T23:19:33.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e01c382d579071dea23a8f8daed1c53d0bf3b164","tid":523434,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T05:58:05.000Z","msg":"上年犯法都入今年數？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}